Name:       Amy Burnett
Course:     CSCI 476 - Parallel Programming
Assignment: Final Project Source Code

=== Usage ==============================================================================

   make
        - Compiles driver program
   ./driver <input_file> <num_threads>
        - Runs the driver program with the given input file and threads

=== Files ==============================================================================

driver.cpp          - driver file that uses the parts of speech implementation
parts_of_speech.hpp - implementation for determining parts of speech
Timer.hpp           - used for timings (created by Dr. Zoppetti)

war_and_peace.txt   - full text of War and Peace, used for testing (~100,000 words)
input10k.txt        - sample text with 10,000 words

dictionary.txt      - sample dictionary that pairs words with parts of speech classifications
